Class Summary
Registration The Registration and Capability API is a part of the Smart Extension API's This API is used by accessory extensions and accessory host applications.
 

Package com.sonyericsson.extras.liveware.aef.registration Description

Provides the classes necessary to register and query Smart Extension API extensions and host applications. Refer to Registration for a detailed description of the Registration & Capabilities API.
